This Chrome extension provides 3D Viewing capabilities for websites developed and/or deployed by 20-20 Technologies Inc.   

Note: When installing this extension, you will receive the following prompt that you must agree to: "20-20 3D Viewer can: access all data on your computer and the websites you visit".  This is a standard cautionary message issued by Chrome for any extension that makes use of the binary Netscape plugin API (NPAPI).

20-20 3D Viewer does not:
•	access the data on your computer
•	access information about the websites you visit
•	collect personal user information
